Proposal due date: 05/05/2022
Proposal overview: Legal Opinion SORA XOR
Proposal goals: A token legal opinion is required for most centralized exchange listings, this proposal requests the funds and due diligence required
Scope of work: 
Share documents and relevant SORA XOR info with an assigned law firm
Current roadblocks and barriers to success: 
XOR could be considered a security under US Securities Law
Evaluation metrics and criteria: 
A legal opinion on XOR is provided, to be used for listing on centralized exchanges and for overall community awareness
Submission requirements: 
Documents of legal entity and white paper
Submission method: https://github.com/sora-xor/rfps/tree/master/open_rfps
Proposed due date: 05 May 2022
Budget amount: $6600 USD
